  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no problem with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could get supplies that we needed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- as I said, the beginning, all we did-- well, we had cooks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we made this gruel for them for a while, until they could digest, and then slowly started on a very limited diet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And like I said, our death rate was tremendous every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The disease that these people had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because we-- we cooperated among ourselves who would take a night shift or a day shift, or-- or we had to work 12 hours, 14 hours.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was just--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What had to be done we did, no matter how many hours we worked or what had-- what had to be done to take care of these people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Oh.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
